# what is markdown?
*markdown is use to style text on the web, is intended to be easy to read to write as is feasible also you can add a link and pic with markdown*
**markdown uses on githup and there is many Markdown syntax that you can use anywhere on GitHub or in your own text files.**
for example:
1. # This is an <h1> tag
2. *This text will be italic*
3. **This text will be bold**
